Author: TOM47
Title: PLANCOIN ICO on January 24 - The cryptocurrency revolution based on Blockchain
Body: Loan feature!  What is Loan feature?  Loan feature at Plancoin could be a completely new trend. This feature will help minimize the risk of facing the big loss of the money they invest. It will also increase the daily trading volume on the Exchanges and help increase the PLAN price.  In general, Loan feature at Plancoin are referred to as margin trading, which is a way to use your BTC or ETH to borrow PLAN directly from the Plancoin website and then trade for profit. It is also a form of “leverage” to help Plancoin develope.  Loan instructions:  Step 1: To start borrowing PLAN, you firstly need to deposit BTC or ETH. The BTC, ETH and PLAN exchange rates will be updated in real time.  Step 2: To apply BTC or ETH deposit to borrow the corresponding PLAN number.  Step 3: You will get PLAN immediately! The fee of borrowing PLAN will be announced in the control panel at Loans and Loans history section. This fee is charged at a normal PLAN of 0.4% per day. You must borrow a minimum of 3 days, and you must pay a fee plus the PLAN you borrowed before the end of the loan period to receive a deposit of BTC or ETH. If the time ends, you don’t pay PLAN, you will not be able to get back the deposit, and then this forces you to own the PLAN.  Why do I have to pay fee for borrowing PLAN?  Normally, any users owning the PLAN can perform staking to get daily interest, so it forces us to charge a fee on the total PLAN you borrow each day. This fee is equivalent to % of staking. In addition, fee collection also increases daily trading volume causing increase PLAN’s value. (Fee of borrowing PLAN may be reduced over time depending on the degree of difficulty or % of profits from daily Staking)  Example: If you make 1 BTC deposit to borrow PLAN within 5 days and the PLAN rate at that time is $ 1.2 / PLAN, then you will receive 7424.675 PLAN. When the loan expires, you need to pay 7424.675 + 2% of fee = 7573.1685 PLAN to receive a deposit.  If you have made a loan, but you didn’t want to trade, or you were experiencing some other problems, you would need to get back the initial deposit. Firstly, you need to withdraw PLAN from the website wallet to wallets on the operating systems to start staking and get daily interest, then about 5 days, you can withdraw the PLAN back to the website wallet to refund the PLAN and get back BTC or ETH that you deposit.  https://medium.com/@plancoin/loan-feature-f4c2d2b1cf66

Author: plancoinico
Title: PLANCOIN ICO on January 24 - The cryptocurrency revolution based on Blockchain
Body: We are eager to introduce you to a great opportunity to invest in the most advanced blockchain platform considered as a “key” technology for digital transformation and the building of future information technology platform.  Our Plancoin’s open source system which operates based on blockchain technology and applies the SCRYPT algorithm is designed to make the process of trading, staking, mining and investing Bitcoin much easier, Plancoin allows you the possibility of a stable income and achieving your financial goals by revealing the opportunities behind this cryptocurrency, a peer to peer digital currency exchanged by using certain principles of cryptography.  Plancoin is a decentralized cryptocurrency, it is a way for users to stay independent of banks, government and all of the taxes, hidden fees, Plancoin are available wherever you need so that you can access with no limitation.    Plancoin allows instant trading, buying and selling of services, transferring money to friends quickly regardless of countries, at extremely low cost and without any interruption, transactions are processed through secure servers with the ability to protect users from all hackers, so users do not have to worry about any related risks.  *PLANCOIN Specification: Coin name: PLANCOIN Coin abbreviation: PLAN Total coin supply: 35,000,000 coins Coinbase maturity: 20 blocks Algorithm: Scrypt Type: PoW/PoS Block reward: 11 coins Target spacing: 64 seconds Target timespan: 1 block Last PoW blocks : 10000 Block age: 11 days Transaction confirmations: 3 blocks  FEATURES: Staking, Lending, Mining, Trading  *ICO details Pre-sale Total: 1,400,000 PLAN Price: $0.42 / 1 PLAN Start: January 18, 2018 (GMT -7) Starting ICO Start: 08:00 AM, January 24, 2018 (GMT -7) End: 09:00 AM, February 23, 2018 (GMT -7) Total: 6,100,000 PLAN The main sale will take place in 30 days with 5 milestones  https://plancoin.co/static_resource/images/misc/ico-price.png  ICO is the capital raising process at PLANCOIN to fund for upgrading, building of functions on Plancoin system as well as ecosystems. In addition, ICO’s  success will be a potent to promote Plancoin to be listed on more exchanges enabling us to run marketing campaigns for brand identity and  successful Plancoin's reputation. Investors will realize  the potential after buying Plancoin as they find  their profits are rising dramatically in both short and long term. In the future, the profit from buying PLANCOIN during your ICO process will increase significantly when PLAN currency  is officially listed on the top exchanges.  * Our Target: Becoming the largest and most popular digital currency exchange channel in the world. In 2018 PLANCOIN will be listed to list on the top exchanges as a plan, In 2019, we will also co-operated with transaction systems, online trading and ecommerce sites to become the leading payment gateway on the world with a 12% market share and then later growth  *Referral and Bonus Program Our 5-level linked referral program allows you to have opportunity to earn a large amount of money by introducing new members to buy coin ICO, you will be received up to 8% bonus on the total number of coins that your members has been purchased, so the more members join, the more money you get. Bonus: Getting $ 5 , when signing up the account by Facebook.  Contact: Website: https://plancoin.co Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/plancoin Twitter: https://twitter.com/plancoin Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwyb8f-1_kIUBbFOUqQ0eUA Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/plancoin Email: support@plancoin.co
